author: jmduarte
body: This PR provides the Higgs Interaction Network Tagger Models in ONNX and (originally) PyTorch. This version of the model was developed using open simulation (https://arxiv.org/abs/1909.12285) and presented in several BTV meetings (e.g. https://indico.cern.ch/event/833434/contributions/3495704/) and JMAR meetings (e.g. https://indico.cern.ch/event/856106/contributions/3613884/).
title: Higgs Interaction Network Tagger Models in ONNX and PyTorch
